ActNational Capital Act
SubjectLease with Allied Properties Real Estate Investment Trust ** NCC **
PrecisOrder authorizing the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to cancel the existing twenty-five year lease ending December 16, 2019, and enter into a new lease for a period of twenty-four years and eleven months, commencing on June 1, 2016, with ALLIED PROPERTIES REAL ESTATE INVESTMENT TRUST to occupy a property located at 40 ELGIN STREET in Ottawa.
